It would've been
better if it was...

36
00:01:46,543 --> 00:01:47,806
Kiel or...

37
00:01:48,712 --> 00:01:49,712
I-

38
00:01:53,299 --> 00:01:54,301
I don't know. You know what?

39
00:01:54,325 --> 00:01:55,993
Whatever. Do whatever you want.

40
00:01:56,970 --> 00:01:59,639
