on a honeymoon?

92
00:05:22,425 --> 00:05:23,425
What are the...

93
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,180
What is this?

94
00:05:32,769 --> 00:05:34,604
Wow! It’s so pretty.

95
00:05:35,271 --> 00:05:39,150
Oh, these flowers
are so beautiful!

96
00:05:39,876 --> 00:05:43,296
