129
00:07:52,909 --> 00:07:54,118
and the shot on target.

130
00:07:55,036 --> 00:07:56,454
If the enemy's in front,

131
00:07:57,246 --> 00:07:59,123
don't fucking hold back.

132
00:09:28,296 --> 00:09:29,296
