know what’s happening.

154
00:11:19,031 --> 00:11:20,241
So no noise.

155
00:11:21,325 --> 00:11:22,325
Copy?

156
00:11:24,870 --> 00:11:27,029
- Let’s go.
- Do you know what time it is?

157
00:11:31,520 --> 00:11:32,730
