166
00:13:06,972 --> 00:13:09,350
Just like you and Kaizer, right?

167
00:13:09,350 --> 00:13:11,769
Who the fuck said
Lamperouge is my best friend?

168
00:13:12,686 --> 00:13:13,687
Isn’t he?

169
00:13:27,159 --> 00:13:28,202
