178
00:14:21,046 --> 00:14:22,326
You won’t learn
anything from me!

179
00:14:24,717 --> 00:14:26,635
Talk, or this bullet
goes through your head.

180
00:14:29,388 --> 00:14:31,015
No matter how much
you try to force me,

181
00:14:32,183 --> 00:14:33,225
you will never know,

182
00:14:33,601 --> 00:14:36,270
