your daughter’s hand.

265
00:19:46,163 --> 00:19:48,290
Why are you asking me?

266
00:19:49,833 --> 00:19:50,833
What?

267
00:19:52,252 --> 00:19:53,254
You should,

268
00:19:53,793 --> 00:19:56,129
