269
00:19:56,154 --> 00:19:58,573
I don't have it.

270
00:19:59,501 --> 00:20:00,501
Wait.

271
00:20:02,471 --> 00:20:05,098
Why do you want to take
my daughter’s hand anyway?

272
00:20:09,645 --> 00:20:10,645
